text: Sidney de Souza (born 28 July 1973) is a Brazilian equestrian. He competed in the team eventing at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Brazil Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Cornélio Procópio
